<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Metastores on Apache Polaris</title><link>https://polaris.apache.org/in-dev/unreleased/metastores/</link><description>Recent content in Metastores on Apache Polaris</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>&lt;a href="https://www.apache.org/"&gt;Copyright © 2026 The Apache Software Foundation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;Licensed under the &lt;a href="https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0"&gt;Apache License, Version 2.0&lt;/a&gt;.</copyright><atom:link href="https://polaris.apache.org/in-dev/unreleased/metastores/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Relational JDBC</title><link>https://polaris.apache.org/in-dev/unreleased/metastores/relational-jdbc/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://polaris.apache.org/in-dev/unreleased/metastores/relational-jdbc/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This implementation leverages Quarkus for datasource management and supports configuration through
environment variables or JVM -D flags at startup. For more information, refer to the &lt;a href="https://quarkus.io/guides/config-reference#env-file"&gt;Quarkus configuration reference&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have 2 options for configuring the persistence backend:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-relational-jdbc-metastore-with-username-and-password" id="1-relational-jdbc-metastore-with-username-and-password"&gt;1. Relational JDBC metastore with username and password&lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#1-relational-jdbc-metastore-with-username-and-password" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using environment variables:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-properties" data-lang="properties"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;POLARIS_PERSISTENCE_TYPE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;relational-jdbc&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;QUARKUS_DATASOURCE_USERNAME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;&amp;lt;your-username&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;QUARKUS_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;&amp;lt;your-password&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;QUARKUS_DATASOURCE_JDBC_URL&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;&amp;lt;jdbc-url-of-postgres&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Using properties file:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>NoSQL MongoDB</title><link>https://polaris.apache.org/in-dev/unreleased/metastores/nosql-mongodb/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://polaris.apache.org/in-dev/unreleased/metastores/nosql-mongodb/</guid><description>&lt;div class="alert alert-info"&gt;&lt;p class="alert-heading"&gt;
 📝 Note&lt;/p&gt;
 The MongoDB backend is currently in &lt;strong&gt;beta&lt;/strong&gt;.
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This implementation uses MongoDB as the persistence backend and leverages the Quarkus MongoDB extension for connection management. Configuration can be done through environment variables or JVM -D flags at startup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="basic-configuration" id="basic-configuration"&gt;Basic Configuration&lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#basic-configuration" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Using environment variables:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-properties" data-lang="properties"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;POLARIS_PERSISTENCE_TYPE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;nosql&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;POLARIS_PERSISTENCE_NOSQL_BACKEND&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;MongoDb&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;QUARKUS_MONGODB_DATABASE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;polaris&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;QUARKUS_MONGODB_CONNECTION_STRING&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;mongodb://&amp;lt;username&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;password&amp;gt;@&amp;lt;host&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;port&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Using properties file:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-properties" data-lang="properties"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;polaris.persistence.type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;nosql&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;polaris.persistence.nosql.backend&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;MongoDb&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;quarkus.mongodb.database&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;polaris&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#c4a000"&gt;quarkus.mongodb.connection-string&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ce5c00;font-weight:bold"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#4e9a06"&gt;mongodb://&amp;lt;username&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;password&amp;gt;@&amp;lt;host&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;port&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="mongodb-atlas-configuration" id="mongodb-atlas-configuration"&gt;MongoDB Atlas Configuration&lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#mongodb-atlas-configuration" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For MongoDB Atlas deployments, use the &lt;code&gt;mongodb+srv://&lt;/code&gt; connection string format:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>